# 4пёЏвѓЈ Next.js Can Do Backend Also

You can write APIs inside the same project.

Example:

```
pages/api/user.js
```

```js
export default function handler(req, res) {
  res.status(200).json({ name: "Venky" });
}
```

URL:

```
localhost:3000/api/user
```

So **Next.js = frontend + backend**.

